OL,4,Cof hospitality businesses out of pocket
OL,6,FIs "dine and dash" the new
OL,7,Fshoplifting? ITV News' North of
OL,8,FEngland Reporter Amy Welch spoke to
OL,9,Fthose affected
OL,11,FA third of hospitality businesses say
OL,12,Fthey've recently experienced an
OL,13,Fincident of "dine and dash" where
OL,14,Fcustomers eat a meal but refuse to pay
OL,15,Ffor it.
