OL,3,CThe rise of 'dine and dash': A third
OL,4,Cof hospitality businesses out of pocket
OL,6,FMany businesses are now fitting CCTV
OL,7,Fcameras and adding additional
OL,8,Fsecurity, but several restaurants told
OL,9,FITV News that they believe people are
OL,10,Fcommitting these crimes because they
OL,11,Fthink they can get away with it.
OL,13,FAnd for restaurants that have only
OL,14,Fjust recovered after struggling
OL,15,Fthrough the pandemic, an unpaid bill
OL,16,Fcan be the difference between making a
OL,17,Fprofit that night and making a loss.
