OL,3,CThe rise of 'dine and dash': A third
OL,4,Cof hospitality businesses out of pocket
OL,6,FIn a statement, the National Police
OL,7,FChiefs' Council told ITV News: "We
OL,8,Fknow that theft can have a significant
OL,9,Fimpact on individuals, businesses and
OL,10,Fcommunities, which is why policing is
OL,11,Fcommitted to tackling all forms of
OL,12,Fthis criminality.
OL,14,F"Dine and dash type offences are
OL,15,Flargely opportunistic in nature and we
OL,16,Fwould encourage all business owners
OL,17,Fand staff to make sure that when they
OL,18,Fdo happen, they are reported so their
OL,19,Flocal force can take action.
